{"tid":541851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"萬寧印花事件，有無人覺得班大愛撚都幾痴線？","createTime":"2018-01-27T01:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T07:03:37.000Z","uid":73883,"like":26,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a4ab65a67af9ba2c33fa78a5f4e6fb8ba59a52","tid":541851,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"一. 法官睇過CCTV提左疑點質疑婆婆有偷野，但大部份人都無睇過片，憑感覺質疑個官有偏頗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n二. 個保安改口供及婆婆好慘77歲仲要做野，同婆婆有無存心偷野係兩件事。好多大愛左膠將啲 information 撈埋晒認為婆婆好慘，所以覺得佢一定無偷野。<br />\n<br />\n三. 未判前大愛撚想借傳媒發聲，令多啲人注意件事及聲討萬寧，到單案判左即刻屌傳媒散庭後追訪婆婆唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/095649_6d4571e54a51e0bdce37fc902fff6a77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F095649_6d4571e54a51e0bdce37fc902fff6a77.png&h=86f95310&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12f5a00fa207d0b290b50f0701304793f82db678","tid":541851,"uid":4213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:59:51.000Z","msg":"又拎條On9笨Son曾出來<br />\n係人都知佢靠呢啲搵食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f3e0ee55873b75cd27c89d0b328eb3855d15ff","tid":541851,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:02:23.000Z","msg":"你都唔接受其他人既意見呀 <br />\n<br />\n你唔痴線 ?"},{"pid":"c5e2d90f5429b667b8a8c04790f8f8cd0e940943","tid":541851,"uid":73883,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"我唔係要針對婆婆，但個官睇左片有以下結論，班大愛撚點解釋？大愛撚又話希望香港保持法治，但當個官睇晒證據得出結論唔啱聽就怪個官，唔係輸打嬴要係乜？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃官指李於自辯時聲稱如沒戴眼鏡，右眼幾近失明（庭上口供是左眼），左眼視力亦只是「矇矇地」，難以看清細小物件。惟黃官自言看過李工作時的閉路電視（CCTV）片段，發現李所述情況與實際有着「令人非常驚訝之差別」，肯定李在庭上說謊。<br />\n<br />\n黃官指李行為非常可疑，例如她將涉案那卷印花放入褲袋後沒有使用，與她自稱當時「必須立即貼着垃圾袋」才誤取印花當膠紙的說法不符。"},{"pid":"d43e85317e46137d7080491a44b9ac15dd405672","tid":541851,"uid":101571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:06:00.000Z","msg":"年紀大嘅人就有光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf346b954522141bbb408346c2551bff5937f2c","tid":541851,"uid":73883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"12f5a00fa207d0b290b50f0701304793f82db678","tid":541851,"uid":4213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T01:59:51.000Z","msg":"又拎條On9笨Son曾出來<br />\n係人都知佢靠呢啲搵食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:09:02.000Z","msg":"借助傳媒力量，咁你要預左散庭一定會有記者追訪，如果唔想咁多記者追，當初唔好搞大件事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bece5535187979a25fecdf2635d9595b73604c6","tid":541851,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:19:38.000Z","msg":"泛民打手未來撚啊廢重痴線<br />\n屌㞗啲討論呢單嘢嘅人唔去屌保蝗黨<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母阿婆印花關我鳩事咩，集中屌柒班奶共狗好過啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/533227/4?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/533227/4?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"e01a2c55b3a248b4a1df7e28fffa27951ff874d1","tid":541851,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:24:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73eca60506614bbcdbc9bc6429b0766040bafbb9","tid":541851,"uid":73883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e01a2c55b3a248b4a1df7e28fffa27951ff874d1","tid":541851,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T02:24:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"關乜事？"},{"pid":"f8bd7901e46175f48853eea7943563ce33597463","tid":541851,"uid":161160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T03:51:50.000Z","msg":"睇完個官既判詞<br />\n我都信阿婆係偷，但應該有人通水佢聽<br />\n先放回原位。"},{"pid":"6beaa44a0b68030af846900612392aad41d85a78","tid":541851,"uid":1067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTim